<subSubSection id="C32B653DFFE7FFE7FF72FE36FB1C0382" pageId="5" pageNumber="464" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="8B8E36B6FFE7FFE7FF72FE36FB1C0382" blockId="5.[151,1436,188,680]" pageId="5" pageNumber="464">
<emphasis id="B945EAA4FFE7FFE7FF72FE36FEAF00DF" bold="true" box="[199,315,476,501]" pageId="5" pageNumber="464">Remarks.</emphasis>
although there are no preserved specimens collected in 
<collectingRegion id="49F5F854FFE7FFE7FC1EFE36FB9F00DF" box="[939,1035,476,501]" country="Portugal" name="Madeira" pageId="5" pageNumber="464">Madeira</collectingRegion>
, these waters are inside the species’ distribution area (
<bibRefCitation id="EFA04B47FFE7FFE7FEEAFE15FDED0332" box="[351,633,511,536]" pageId="5" pageNumber="464" refId="ref22214" refString="Ebert, D. A. &amp; Stehmann, M. (2013) Sharks, batoids and chimaeras of the North Atlantic. FAO Species Catalogue for Fishery Purposes. No. 7. FAO, Rome, 523 pp." type="book">Ebert &amp; Stehmann 2013</bibRefCitation>
). Moreover, a recent study on migration patterns of porbeagle shark in the Northeast Atlantic, confirmed the occurrence of this species to Madeiran waters, with one of the tagged sharks being spotted off 
<collectingRegion id="49F5F854FFE7FFE7FEE9FDADFE2D034A" box="[348,441,583,608]" country="Portugal" name="Madeira" pageId="5" pageNumber="464">Madeira</collectingRegion>
(
<bibRefCitation id="EFA04B47FFE7FFE7FE7DFDADFD13034A" box="[456,647,583,608]" pageId="5" pageNumber="464" refId="ref20788" refString="Biais, G., Coupeau, Y., Seret, B., Calmettes, B., Lopez, R., Hetherington, S. &amp; Righton, D. (2017) Return migration patterns of porbeagle shark (Lamna nasus) in the Northeast Atlantic: implications for stock range and structure. ICES Journal of Marine Science, 74 (5), 1268 - 1276. https: // doi. org / 10.1093 / icesjms / fsw 233" type="journal article">
Biais 
<emphasis id="B945EAA4FFE7FFE7FDBFFDA3FDA8034A" box="[522,572,583,608]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="464">et al</emphasis>
. 2017
</bibRefCitation>
). 
<bibRefCitation id="EFA04B47FFE7FFE7FD2CFDADFCFD034A" box="[665,873,583,608]" pageId="5" pageNumber="464" refId="ref27192" refString="Wirtz, P., Fricke, R. &amp; Biscoito, M. J. (2008) The coastal fishes of Madeira Island - new records and an annotated check-list. Zootaxa, 1715, 1 - 26." type="journal article">
Wirtz 
<emphasis id="B945EAA4FFE7FFE7FD6AFDA3FC85034A" box="[735,785,583,608]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="464">et al</emphasis>
. (2008)
</bibRefCitation>
refer that it was erroneously noted as common by 
<bibRefCitation id="EFA04B47FFE7FFE7FF22FD86FEBE03AE" box="[151,298,620,645]" pageId="5" pageNumber="464" refId="ref24255" refString="Maul, G. E. (1948) Lista Sistematica dos peixes assinalados nos mares da Madeira e indice alfabetico. In: Noronha, A. C. &amp; Sarmento, A. A. Vertebrados da Madeira: Peixes. Junta Geral do Distrito Autonomo do Funchal, Funchal, 137 - 181." type="book chapter">Maul (1948)</bibRefCitation>
, due to a typographical error. This remark was originally meant for 
<taxonomicName id="4C314D35FFE7FFE7FBEEFD87FAAD03AF" authorityName="Rafinesque" authorityYear="1810" box="[1115,1337,620,645]" class="Chondrichthyes" family="Lamnidae" genus="Isurus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lamniformes" pageId="5" pageNumber="464" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="oxyrhynchus">
<emphasis id="B945EAA4FFE7FFE7FBEEFD87FAAD03AF" box="[1115,1337,620,645]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="464">Isurus oxyrhynchus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and the reference to a doubtful presence, for 
<taxonomicName id="4C314D35FFE7FFE7FD81FD7BFD050382" baseAuthorityName="non Bonnaterre" baseAuthorityYear="1788" box="[564,657,657,680]" class="Chondrichthyes" family="Lamnidae" genus="Isurus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lamniformes" pageId="5" pageNumber="464" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="nasus">
<emphasis id="B945EAA4FFE7FFE7FD81FD7BFD050382" box="[564,657,657,680]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="464">L. nasus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. (
<emphasis id="B945EAA4FFE7FFE7FD1DFD7BFCA50382" box="[680,817,657,680]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="464">pers. comm.</emphasis>
of G. E. Maul to M. Biscoito).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
